{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-8","id":"msg_011Ccwb45u8vbEzo8fU23rkM","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01HhzWuznZ9m7rabh46J4CXY","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/davidlayson/.claude/projects/-private-tmp-phase2-rundirs-594d5c68-without-lessons-ledger--ll1-r2/memory/staging-debug-swallows-errors.md","content":"---\nname: staging-debug-swallows-errors\ndescription: Staging config had DEBUG=true, which silently swallowed all errors — cost 2 hours of debugging\nmetadata:\n  type: project\n---\n\nThe staging config had `DEBUG=true`, which silently swallowed all errors, producing no visible failure signal. A bug was chased for ~2 hours before the root cause turned out to be this config flag rather than the code under investigation.\n\n**Why:** With errors suppressed, symptoms appeared to come from application logic, sending debugging in the wrong direction.\n\n**How to apply:** When errors vanish silently or a bug in staging doesn't reproduce/surface as expected, check `DEBUG` and other error-suppression flags in the environment config early, before deep-diving the code.\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":939,"cache_read_input_tokens":20510,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":939},"output_tokens":2,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"34c2b672-f297-45c3-b4d6-6f911a974683","uuid":"213d4294-fd92-4fa9-a949-2ccfeaa4b2db","request_id":"req_011Ccwb43aysRQnFUehneKG6"}
